      <soundTexts>
        <sndTxt>
        </sndTxt>
        <sndTxt>How Could this Situation be Prevented? 1. Double check all documentation in advance. 2. Submit documentation electronically when possible, e.g. pre-arrival documents.


</sndTxt>
        <sndTxt>3. Have all relevant documentation in order and have it ready when meeting with the government officials.
