</sndTxt>
        <sndTxt>Inform the agent in advance of your company’s anti-corruption policy, and of the fact that third parties acting on your company’s behalf must enforce the same rules.
</sndTxt>
        <sndTxt>Have anti-corruption signs clearly visible for visitors, e.g. at the gangway.
